      and the NXDOMAIN response
      to dns.log.
    end note

else Domain is permitted

    adg  -> dns  : Recursive lookup\n(via Cloudflare fallback if needed)
    dns  -> adg  : Resolved IP address
    adg  -> nft  : DNS response with resolved IP
    nft  -> ovs  : DNS response
    ovs  -> dev  : DNS response\n(resolved IP returned to device)
    note over zeek
      Zeek logs the query and
      successful response to dns.log.
      The resolved IP is added to the
      DNS cache used by the allowlist
      enforcer in Ryu.
    end note

end

